Package: TDMM
Type: Package
Title: Bayesian Time-Dynamic Mixed-Effects Models
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Makena", "Grigsby", email = "makenavgrigsby@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Esra", "Kurum", role = "aut")
)
Description: Fits Bayesian time-dynamic mixed-effects models for longitudinal
    data using JAGS. The package currently supports Gaussian, Bernoulli, and
    Poisson outcomes with spline-based time-varying coefficient functions and
    subject-level random effects.
License: MIT
